#生成music乐谱并进行播放。
song = 
  Music()+
  Meter(4,4)+
  Key(1)+
  Line(c(g10pit,g20pit,g30pit,g48pit),
       c(g10dur,g20dur,g30dur,g48dur),
       c(g10tie,g20tie,g30tie,g48tie))+
  Line(c(f10pit,f20pit,f30pit,f48pit),
       c(f10dur,f20dur,f30dur,f48dur),
       c(f48tie))+
  Clef('G',to=1)+
  Clef('F',to=2)+
  Tempo(85)

show(song,to = c("score", "audio"))
